# .cursor/rules/902-report-automation.mdc
version: 1.0.0
name: Report Automation
description: Automated security report generation and management
globs: ["*"]
triggers: ["on_scan_complete"]

<workflow>
Report automation handles the following:

1. Report Structure
- Executive Summary
- Technical Findings
- Risk Assessment
- Remediation Steps

2. Integration Points
- Issue Tracking System
- CI/CD Pipeline
- Security Dashboard

3. Notification System
- Team Alerts
- Management Reports
- Compliance Updates

4. Documentation
- Audit Trail
- Evidence Collection
- Compliance Mapping
</workflow>